{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b4d3e4905c","title":"“肃反的方法是错误的”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a9b50c9f5c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"b4d3e4905c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0161aa7fe8","name":"沈阳药学院"},{"id":"ca42db278d","name":"尹鲁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"773838f3da","type":"title","text":"“肃反的方法是错误的”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b4d3e4905c"},{"id":"31f6e7d407","type":"authors","text":"沈阳药学院尹鲁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b4d3e4905c"},{"id":"98a8326cd9","type":"subtitle","text":"(尹鲁：沈阳药学院讲师)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b4d3e4905c"},{"id":"9add18edb5","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反是完全应该的，但在我看来，那次肃反的方法是错误的，缺点大于成绩，伤害了许多人的积极性。为了说明他的看法，他做了这样一个比喻：一个人的身上有块疮，如果用火来烧，细菌当然烧死了，可是连人也一起烧死了。他向记者说：你说是烧死细菌是主要的，还是烧死人是主要的?所以会这样，是因为没有接受“三反”“五反”教训的结果。不采取群众运动的办法也完全可以把反革命肃清。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b4d3e4905c"},{"id":"baf3b5032c","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《团结起来把右派分子的斗争进行到底》","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b4d3e4905c"}],"page":{"id":"49c47ae6a5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b4d3e4905c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}